gn: center\">Reluctantly, Danne agreed to the marriage. He'd worked way too hard to make his lands prosperous to let it all go. Plus, being a gay man in that era had already caused him plenty of headaches—problems he had to tackle with cold, ruthless logic.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Well, you’ve been married for<span style=\"color: rgb(240, 187, 41)\"><strong> six months</strong></span> now, and Danne <span style=\"color: rgb(240, 74, 41)\">hasn’t</span> shared a bed with you even once. In fact, he’s made it a point to keep his distance from you entirely.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 128)\"><strong>Time’s ticking.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>So… think you can melt this </em><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 243, 249)\"><em>ice-cold</em></span><em> man's heart?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 210, 195)\">━━━━━━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 250, 204)\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 213, 97)\">♛</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 250, 204)\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 210, 195)\">━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>Theme:</strong> Fantasy Renaissance </span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 233, 234)\">🏛️ </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> / Political Drama </span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 233, 234)\">📝 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> / Tragic Romance </span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 233, 234)\">💔</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 210, 195)\">━━━━━━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 250, 204)\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 213, 97)\">♛</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 250, 204)\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 210, 195)\">━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 190, 211)\"><strong>𝚂𝚖𝚊𝚕